		"description": "<p><strong>Reach 1</strong> <em>(Requires 1+ Mana Dice)</em></p><p>Deal damage equal to <strong>2× (sum of Mana Dice + STR)</strong>. Treat Heavy armor as Medium, and Medium as unarmored.</p><p><strong>Upgrades:</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Stabilized Mana Core.</strong> Roll Mana Dice with advantage.</li><li><strong>Arc Module.</strong> (1/round) Strike +1 target adjacent to the first.</li><li><strong>Streamlined Ignition.</strong> –3 to repair DC. If you roll 20+ on the repair check, gain 1 action back.</li></ul><p><strong>Mishap — Arcane Rebound:</strong> After the attack, suffer damage equal to the sum rolled. The blade becomes inoperable (DC 12 Arcana check to fix).</p><p><em>Selecting this invention adds the matching item to your inventory; the item itself carries the attack/defense effects and upgrades.</em></p>",
